{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Three Kingdoms Front is an idle text game based on the Three Kingdoms. At the beginning of the game, you have to choose a team to start the adventure. The characters in the team are composed of generals from the Three Kingdoms. As the game progresses, the system will randomly trigger various events, and automatically trigger various military orders and various internal affairs facilities according to different development situations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Featured system: Welfare system: Generals can be drawn for free every day, 2 ordinary draws, 1 advanced draw</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Recruitment system: Triggered by each battle victory, there are all kinds of top-quality generals</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Placement system: Use high internal affairs charm for development, high intelligence and force for war, and place generals reasonably to maximize the benefits</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Battle system: The more battles you challenge, in addition to the higher silver income every day, you will also have the opportunity to recruit more top-quality generals.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2946280/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738985670","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2946280/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1738985670","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2946280/290151d94736e99b0968429097d9cee3a0669db3/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738985670","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2946280/290151d94736e99b0968429097d9cee3a0669db3/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738985670","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"In-App Purchases","id":35}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Three Kingdoms Front is an idle text game based on the Three Kingd